text.text:
Hey, I need some air. Point that air at me.
Go into the glove compartment.
I'm making a hard right at Saratoga.
See if they're still on us.
No flipping way.
Just act natural.
Do you have any idea of how fast you were going?
I'm pretty sure I was below ten above the speed limit.
You have a busted tail light. Have you noticed?
I don't see anything.
Are you under influence of any drugs or alcohol?
Uh, let me check.
I don't want to do this, but we gotta dump the quaaludes.
(Dumps quaaludes)
